<p>- <strong>Consistency</strong>: Avoid fluctuations; stable temperature is key to preventing premature aging.</p>
<p>- <strong>Cooling System</strong>: Invest in a reliable wine cellar cooling system to maintain consistent
  temperatures.</p>
<p><strong>Humidity Levels</strong></p>
<p>- <strong>Ideal Range</strong>: Maintain humidity between 60% to 70%.</p>
<p>- <strong>Why Important</strong>: Proper humidity prevents corks from drying out and shrinking, which can lead to
